✔ Crackling / Popping
  - Buffer size too small
  - CPU overload
  - Priority issues
✔ Buffer overrun / underrun (Xruns)
  - Increase buffer size
  - Fix scheduling issues
✔ No audio output
  - Check ALSA device
  - Check volume/mute
  - Check routing
✔ High latency
  - Reduce buffer size
  - Use real-time scheduling
✔ Audio sync issues
  - Timestamp management
  - Clock synchronization

