10.1 Must-Practice Audio Coding Problems ⭐⭐⭐

1. ⭐⭐⭐ CIRCULAR/RING BUFFER (MOST ASKED)
   Implement thread-safe circular buffer from scratch
   - Single producer, single consumer
   - Multiple producers, multiple consumers
   - Lock-free version using atomics

2. ⭐⭐⭐ AUDIO MIXER
   Implement audio sample mixer
   - Mix two audio streams
   - Handle different sample rates
   - Volume control per stream

3. ⭐⭐⭐ PRODUCER-CONSUMER AUDIO PIPELINE
   Multi-threaded audio streaming
   - Producer fills buffer
   - Consumer reads and plays
   - Handle synchronization

4. ⭐⭐⭐ AUDIO BUFFER OVERFLOW/UNDERFLOW DETECTION
   Detect and handle xruns

5. ⭐⭐⭐ SAMPLE RATE CONVERSION
